<bibRefCitation author="ULRICH E. O." box="[997,1140,1557,1583]" pageId="13" pageNumber="574" pagination="233 - 257" refId="ref23063" refString="ULRICH E. O. 1882. - American Palaeozoic Bryozoa. The Journal of the Cincinnati Society of Natural History 5: 121 - 175, 233 - 257." type="journal article" year="1882">Ulrich, 1882</bibRefCitation>
</taxonomicName>
by abundant diaphragms in autozooecia, more angular apertural shape and two kinds of acanthostyles.
</paragraph>
